baseline_texts: The frame shows an open wooden jewelry box placed on a floral-patterned surface. Inside the box, there are several pieces of jewelry, including a blue and purple beaded necklace and a chain or bracelet. The inside lid of the jewelry box has a mirror, reflecting some of the contents. The overall setting suggests a personal or decorative display of jewelry items.

This frame shows an open jewelry box placed on a fabric surface with a floral pattern. Inside the jewelry box, there is a mirror on the lid. The interior contains several pieces of jewelry, including what appears to be a bracelet made of blue beads, a string of pearls or similar beads, and other small jewelry items. The background surface appears to be a patterned cloth or bedspread, and part of a carpeted floor is also visible.

This frame shows a small wooden jewelry box with an open lid that has a mirror on the inside. Inside the box, there are multiple pieces of jewelry including a black bracelet on the left, a silver bracelet or watch, and two beaded necklaces - one with blue beads and the other with metallic beads. The box is resting on a fabric surface with a floral pattern.

The image shows a dark wooden jewelry box with a mirror on the inside of the lid. The box is open and contains a flexible beaded bracelet with beads in alternating blue and greenish colors, a ring with a pink stone, and a dark circular band or ring. The background appears to be a patterned fabric surface in muted earth-tone colors. A hand is reaching towards the jewelry box from the top right corner of the image.

This image shows a hand with green-painted nails holding open a small wooden jewelry box with a glass mirror on the inside of the lid. Inside the box, there are several pieces of jewelry including a black ring on the left, a silver ring, and a beaded necklace or bracelet with blue and green beads arranged in a circular pattern. The jewelry box is resting on a fabric surface with a floral pattern. The reflection in the mirror shows a similar view of the objects inside the box.

The frame shows a close-up of a person's hand opening a small, rectangular wooden jewelry box with a hinged lid. Inside the box, there are various pieces of jewelry, including a blue beaded necklace, a ring, and a bracelet or chain. The jewelry box is placed on a patterned fabric surface. The person's fingernails are painted light blue.

The image shows a close-up of a hand reaching towards or touching a small, rectangular wooden box with a floral inlay design on the lid. The box is resting on a surface covered by a patterned fabric, which appears to have a leafy or floral design. The background shows a portion of a carpeted floor and possibly a foot or shoe. The lighting is dim but sufficient to see the details on the box and the hand clearly.

The image shows a wooden box with intricate inlay work on the lid, placed on a patterned surface, possibly a tablecloth or fabric. The inlay features a design of leaves and what looks like a bird perched on a branch. In the top right corner of the frame, a hand is moving, slightly blurred due to motion. The overall setting suggests a decorative or handcrafted item in focus.
